#: templates/matches/home.html:5
msgid "Rugby predictions"
msgstr "Pronostics rugby"

#: templates/matches/home.html:13
msgid "The first rugby predictions app is here!"
msgstr "La première appli de pronostics rugby est disponible !"

#: templates/matches/home.html:14
msgid ""
"Week after week, predict unlikely scores and rack up points against your "
"friends."
msgstr ""
"Journée après journée, prédis des scores improbables et marque des points "
"face à tes potes."

#: templates/matches/home.html:15
msgid "Don't wait any longer — sign up to join us."
msgstr "Alors n'hésite plus, inscris-toi pour nous rejoindre."

#: templates/matches/home.html:31
msgid "Oval'Pronos — simple and fun"
msgstr "Oval'Pronos, c'est simple et c'est drôle"

#: templates/matches/home.html:32
msgid "You don't need to be a rugby expert to play!"
msgstr "Pas besoin d'être un crack du rugby pour jouer !"

#: templates/matches/home.html:33
msgid "Every week, make predictions with friends and get live results."
msgstr "Chaque semaine, tu pronostiques avec tes potes et tu as les résultats en direct."

#: templates/matches/home.html:40
msgid "Predict matches"
msgstr "Pronostique tes matchs"

#: templates/matches/home.html:41
msgid ""
"The odds system rewards risk-takers. The more precise your prediction, the "
"more points you earn."
msgstr ""
"Le système de cotes récompense les prises de risque. Plus ton pronostic "
"est précis, plus tu marques de points."

#: templates/matches/home.html:42
msgid ""
"Create or join a private league with your invite code and challenge your "
"friends."
msgstr ""
"Crée ou rejoins une ligue privée avec ton code d'invitation et affronte "
"tes amis."

#: templates/matches/rules.html:4
msgid "Scoring rules"
msgstr "Règles du jeu"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:10
msgid "Crouch, bind, set"
msgstr "Flexion, liez, jeu"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:11
msgid "How does the scoring system work?"
msgstr "Comment fonctionne le système de points ?"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:14
msgid "Scoring tiers"
msgstr "Le barème"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:21
msgid "Odds × 3"
msgstr "Cote × 3"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:29
msgid "Odds × 2"
msgstr "Cote × 2"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:37
msgid "Odds × 1"
msgstr "Cote × 1"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:45
msgid "point"
msgstr "point"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:52
msgid "Odds"
msgstr "Les cotes"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:54
msgid ""
"Odds are based on Unibet odds (multiplied by 10 to avoid decimals). A match "
"with high odds on the winner scores more points, but you take more risk."
msgstr ""
"Les cotes sont basées sur les cotes Unibet (multipliées par 10 pour éviter "
"les décimales). Un match avec une forte cote sur le vainqueur rapporte plus "
"de points, mais tu prends plus de risque."

#: templates/matches/rules.html:58
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Exemple"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:60
msgid ""
"Clermont — Perpignan, Perpignan odds: 63 (= 6.3 at Unibet), good gap "
"threshold: 3 pts"
msgstr ""
"Clermont — Perpignan, cote Perpignan : 63 (= 6,3 chez Unibet), seuil bon "
"écart : 3 pts"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:68
msgid "Actual score"
msgstr "Score réel"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:69
msgid "Result"
msgstr "Résultat"

#: templates/matches/rules.html:70 templates/rankings/index.html:20
msgid "Points"
